# Weibull

> Weibull distribution.

<section class="usage">

## Usage

```javascript
var weibull = require( '@stdlib/math/base/dists/weibull' );
```

#### weibull

Weibull distribution.

```javascript
var dist = weibull;
// returns {...}
```
